Edits applied to [content/papers/history.md](/home/dave/Projects/jaynes-archive/content/papers/history.md).

Summary of changes:
- Improved markdown structure for cleaner rendering by adding consistent blank lines around section headers.
- Normalized in-text citations to markdown footnote references (e.g., converted parenthetical citation patterns to `[^...]` style).
- Converted the `## REFERENCES` block into proper markdown footnote definitions matching those in-text citations.
- Fixed one malformed prose fragment (`R \>"> a` -> `R >> a`) that affected readability/rendering.
- Confirmed no duplicate abstract text in body, no tables to repair, and no math/LaTeX content was modified.
